doc ///
    Key
        dynkinToPartition
	(dynkinToPartition,List)
    Headline
        converts a highest weight written in the basis of fundamental dominant weights for type A into a partition
    Usage
        dynkinToPartition(lambda)
    Inputs 
        lambda:List
    Outputs
